{"tid":1080592,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做人真係好攰","createTime":"2019-03-27T16:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T13:49:06.000Z","uid":199279,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2342c292586c85e93ff526ffb3d162f7d4330550","tid":1080592,"uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:49:44.000Z","msg":"晚晚12點鐘上床<br />\n望住個天花板望到3 4點先瞓<br />\n一上張床就會喺度喊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日頭就做咩都無動力 望住個路軌就好想跳落去<br />\n做錯嘢 成日比人鬧on9 份人又蠢又唔識解決問題<br />\n好怕見到人 但係為咗attendance就喺度迫自己翻學<br />\n身邊無朋友會聽我呻 唔想屋企人擔心所以唔同佢地講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知呢啲係咪叫壓力大 <br />\n最近爛咗幾份midterm 温咗好耐都唔知點解考到成pat屎<br />\n天資唔夠聰明 無其他人咁醒 <br />\n學校就比fd笑 翻工就比boss鬧<br />\n我真係好辛苦 成日都好唔開心<br />\n人地叫我開心啲 唔好咁負面 <br />\n我都想 但係我做唔到 因為無咩值得我去開心 無人同我溝通 無咩好嘢發生喺我身上<br />\n<br />\n知道自己有問題 已經book咗counselling 但係怕自己未捱到嗰日就已經撐唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都好想堅強啲 好想靠自己解決問題"},{"pid":"97cab66278b526fc107385113991253614fe0ff5","tid":1080592,"uid":199279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"點解個個身邊都有朋友 會互相幫對方<br />\n點解我比個真心對人 但係人地對我淨係工具<br />\n佢地expect我會識<br />\n我唔識嘅 就會話 你好好反省下自己點解做唔到我個fd啦<br />\n我真係meet唔到你地心入面嘅expectatIons<br />\n好對唔住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ca84b72c18979234857891c17cba161f2c22e9","tid":1080592,"uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"點解個個人上到大學都有佢地嘅ulife<br />\n但係我就永遠自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實日日自己食飯好慘㗎<br />\n好似比人望住咁<br />\n揾個摺少少嘅can 都會撞到熟人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似連食飯都有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532fe30cdcbaea4555ff0c358a8dfe1cdcab499e","tid":1080592,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:04:15.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"e09cd30ce8e3ae39c26d79fd5fd08d01ce6c3b7f","tid":1080592,"uid":143435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"合格就得啦 唔洗太chur自己既，aim high係好，但壓力太大就要暫停啦"},{"pid":"38325e0a08422c9e446af78db2730730e00fb6c8","tid":1080592,"uid":76420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe0b2e19c9be3ec5d9ae717aa8a2fa65573df7b","tid":1080592,"uid":44435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c581ec738c59f9e54593b27a35f334703e02fa5","tid":1080592,"uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09cd30ce8e3ae39c26d79fd5fd08d01ce6c3b7f","tid":1080592,"uid":143435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"合格就得啦 唔洗太chur自己既，aim high係好，但壓力太大就要暫停啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"要chur gpa揀major<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我根本就無呢種天份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d847f6fdc1bfb94feb20a5b9999947b5f538d78","tid":1080592,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T18:10:31.000Z","msg":"至少你有上莊 大把朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd9285d15abbdc3f5f56ce91ae8563c76e7da1f","tid":1080592,"uid":222678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T18:11:33.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔知講咩安慰你好 但係希望你唔好咁絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0b4d427f1a67621b49b4bb00c1ce781d0ccccd","tid":1080592,"uid":211657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T18:13:21.000Z","msg":"我同意 真係好攰<br />\n攰得嚟又瞓唔著 朝頭早又冇精神<br />\n究竟呢種生活要持續到幾時"},{"pid":"472e2fd4430725f98487d1d552ba95ff1